songs.title: Sticcs (2)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Ha, yeah
Neighbor gang, yeah, yeah, ha
In this bitch with my motherfuckin' niggas
Clay, told 'em, hmm, hmm

[Chorus]
(Sticks, sticks) Thirty round mag (Sticks)
Fifty round drum (Sticks), quit playin' dumb (Bitch)
The M where I'm from (Bitch, word), the pinky and thumb (Bitch, that's how I'm movin')
I'm countin' up sums (Bitch), you live with your moms (Bitch)

[Verse]
My cousin Saddam (Word), he taught me how to create bombs (Boom)
I made the bread out of crumbs (Yeah), I did anything to feed my moms (Uh)
I'm smokin' gas out a bong (Gas), one hit of this shit'll fuck up your lungs (Uh)
I fuck a bitch if she sprung, she want a nigga on tip of her tongue (Woah, woah, woah)
Check out these diamond teeth (Shinin'), a-a-a-all of my jewelry, this shit is unique (Bling)
I might drop a duece for the piece, I just copped the coupe just to drive down the street (Skrt)
And you got a maximum, leased, got work but you taxin' your peeps
And I came a long way from McDonalds 'cause I was the one with the spatula, sheesh (Ha)

[Chorus]
(Sticks, sticks) Thirty round mag (Sticks)
Fifty round drum (Sticks), quit playin' dumb (Bitch)
The M where I'm from (Bitch, word), the pinky and thumb (Bitch, that's how I'm movin')
I'm countin' up sums (Bitch), you live with your moms (Bitch)
(St-st-sticks, sticks) Thirty round mag (Sticks)
Fifty round drum (Sticks), quit playin' dumb (Bitch)
